{"data":[{"name":"70:1","price":"1. (நபியே! நிராகரிப்பவர்களுக்குச்) சம்பவிக்கக்கூடிய வேதனையைப் பற்றி கேட்பவன் ஒருவன் (உம்மிடம் அது) எப்பொழுது வருமென(ப் பரிகாசமாக)க் கேட்கிறான்.","arabic":"سَأَلَ سَآئِلُۢ بِعَذَابٖ وَاقِعٖ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5376,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"sa-ala sāilun biʿadhābin wāqiʿin ","translations":["Asked","a questioner","about a punishment","bound to happen","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["sa-ala","sāilun","biʿadhābin","wāqiʿin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,720],[2,720,3789],[3,3789,6089],[4,6089,7264]]}},{"name":"70:2","price":"2. நிராகரிப்பவர்களுக்கு (அது சம்பவிக்கும் சமயத்தில்) அதைத் தடுத்து விடக்கூடியவன் ஒருவனுமில்லை.","arabic":"لِّلۡكَٰفِرِينَ لَيۡسَ لَهُۥ دَافِعٞ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5377,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"lil'kāfirīna laysa lahu dāfiʿun ","translations":["To the disbelievers","not","of it","any preventer","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["lil'kāfirīna","laysa","lahu","dāfiʿun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1730],[2,1730,2520],[3,2520,3080],[4,3080,4395]]}},{"name":"70:3","price":"3. உயர்ப் பாதைகளையுடைய அல்லாஹ்வினால் (அது சம்பவிக்கும்).","arabic":"مِّنَ ٱللَّهِ ذِي ٱلۡمَعَارِجِ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5378,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"mina al-lahi dhī al-maʿāriji ","translations":["From","Allah","Owner","(of) the ways of ascent","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["mina","al-lahi","dhī","al-maʿāriji",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,400],[2,400,1430],[3,1430,1620],[4,1620,2935]]}},{"name":"70:4","price":"4. அந்நாளில் வானவர்களும், ஜிப்ரயீலும் அவனிடம் போய்ச் சேருவார்கள். (அந்நாள்) ஐம்பதினாயிரம் வருடங்களுக்குச் சமமாக இருக்கும்.","arabic":"تَعۡرُجُ ٱلۡمَلَٰٓئِكَةُ وَٱلرُّوحُ إِلَيۡهِ فِي يَوۡمٖ كَانَ مِقۡدَارُهُۥ خَمۡسِينَ أَلۡفَ سَنَةٖ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5379,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"taʿruju al-malāikatu wal-rūḥu ilayhi fī yawmin kāna miq'dāruhu khamsīna alfa sanatin ","translations":["Ascend","the Angels","and the Spirit","to Him","in","a Day","[is]","its measure","(is) fifty","thousand","year(s)","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["taʿruju","al-malāikatu","wal-rūḥu","ilayhi","fī","yawmin","kāna","miq'dāruhu","khamsīna","alfa","sanatin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,870],[2,870,3970],[3,3970,4970],[4,4970,5780],[5,5780,6210],[6,6210,7900],[7,7900,8480],[8,8480,9920],[9,9920,10990],[10,10990,11580],[11,11580,12765]]}},{"name":"70:5","price":"5. (நபியே!) நீர் நேர்த்தியான சாந்தத்தோடு பொறுத்திருப்பீராக!","arabic":"فَٱصۡبِرۡ صَبۡرٗا جَمِيلًا","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5380,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-iṣ'bir ṣabran jamīlan ","translations":["So be patient","a patience","good","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-iṣ'bir","ṣabran","jamīlan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,780],[2,780,2270],[3,2270,3965]]}},{"name":"70:6","price":"6. (எனினும்,) நிச்சயமாக அவர்கள் அதை வெகு தூரமாக எண்ணுகின்றனர். ","arabic":"إِنَّهُمۡ يَرَوۡنَهُۥ بَعِيدٗا","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5381,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"innahum yarawnahu baʿīdan ","translations":["Indeed, they","see it","(as) far off","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["innahum","yarawnahu","baʿīdan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1680],[2,1680,2910],[3,2910,4165]]}},{"name":"70:7","price":"7. நாமோ அதை வெகு சமீபமாகக் காண்கிறோம்.","arabic":"وَنَرَىٰهُ قَرِيبٗا","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5382,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wanarāhu qarīban ","translations":["But We see it","near","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["wanarāhu","qarīban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1120],[2,1120,2705]]}},{"name":"70:8","price":"8. அந்நாளில் வானம் பழுக்கக் காய்ந்த செம்பைப்போல் ஆகிவிடும்.","arabic":"يَوۡمَ تَكُونُ ٱلسَّمَآءُ كَٱلۡمُهۡلِ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5383,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"yawma takūnu al-samāu kal-muh'li ","translations":["(The) Day ","will be","the sky","like molten copper","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["yawma","takūnu","al-samāu","kal-muh'li",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,610],[2,610,1460],[3,1460,3880],[4,3880,5275]]}},{"name":"70:9","price":"9. மலைகள் பஞ்சைப் போல் ஆகி (பறந்து) விடும்.","arabic":"وَتَكُونُ ٱلۡجِبَالُ كَٱلۡعِهۡنِ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5384,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"watakūnu al-jibālu kal-ʿih'ni ","translations":["And will be","the mountains","like wool","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["watakūnu","al-jibālu","kal-ʿih'ni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1020],[2,1020,2150],[3,2150,3525]]}},{"name":"70:10","price":"10. ஒரு நண்பன் மற்றொரு நண்பனை(ப் பார்த்த போதிலும் அவனுடைய சுகத்தை) விசாரிக்க மாட்டான்.","arabic":"وَلَا يَسۡـَٔلُ حَمِيمٌ حَمِيمٗا","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5385,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"walā yasalu ḥamīmun ḥamīman ","translations":["And not","will ask","a friend","(about) a friend","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["walā","yasalu","ḥamīmun","ḥamīman",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,650],[2,650,1430],[3,1430,2460],[4,2460,4095]]}},{"name":"70:11","price":"11. அவர்கள் ஒருவர் மற்றவரைப் பார்த்துக் கொள்வார்கள். குற்றவாளி, அந்நாளில் தன் வேதனைக்குப் பரிகாரமாகத் தன் பிள்ளைகளையும்,","arabic":"يُبَصَّرُونَهُمۡۚ يَوَدُّ ٱلۡمُجۡرِمُ لَوۡ يَفۡتَدِي مِنۡ عَذَابِ يَوۡمِئِذِۭ بِبَنِيهِ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5386,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"yubaṣṣarūnahum yawaddu al-muj'rimu law yaftadī min ʿadhābi yawmi-idhin bibanīhi ","translations":["They will be made to see each other","Would wish","the criminal","if","he (could be) ransomed","from","(the) punishment","(of) that Day","by his children","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["yubaṣṣarūnahum","yawaddu","al-muj'rimu","law","yaftadī","min","ʿadhābi","yawmi-idhin","bibanīhi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2540],[2,2540,3300],[3,3300,4290],[4,4290,4680],[5,4680,5750],[6,5750,6080],[7,6080,6940],[8,6940,8870],[9,8870,12485]]}},{"name":"70:12","price":"12. தன் மனைவிகளையும், தன் சகோதரனையும்,","arabic":"وَصَٰحِبَتِهِۦ وَأَخِيهِ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5387,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"waṣāḥibatihi wa-akhīhi ","translations":["And his spouse","and his brother","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["waṣāḥibatihi","wa-akhīhi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1810],[2,1810,4775]]}},{"name":"70:13","price":"13. தன்னை ஆதரித்து வந்த தன் சொந்தக்காரர்களையும்,","arabic":"وَفَصِيلَتِهِ ٱلَّتِي تُـٔۡوِيهِ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5388,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wafaṣīlatihi allatī tu'wīhi ","translations":["And his nearest kindred","who","sheltered him","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["wafaṣīlatihi","allatī","tu'wīhi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1570],[2,1570,2420],[3,2420,5215]]}},{"name":"70:14","price":"14. இன்னும், பூமியிலுள்ள அனைத்தையுமே கொடுத்தேனும் தன்னைக் காப்பாற்றிக்கொள்ளப் பிரியப்படுவான்.","arabic":"وَمَن فِي ٱلۡأَرۡضِ جَمِيعٗا ثُمَّ يُنجِيهِ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5389,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"waman fī al-arḍi jamīʿan thumma yunjīhi ","translations":["And whoever","(is) on","the earth","all","then","it (could) save him","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["waman","fī","al-arḍi","jamīʿan","thumma","yunjīhi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1190],[2,1190,1440],[3,1440,2260],[4,2260,4089],[5,4089,5439],[6,5439,9824]]}},{"name":"70:15","price":"15. (எனினும்) அது ஆகக்கூடியதல்ல. நிச்சயமாக அது நரகத்தின் நெருப்பு. (இவனைச் சூழ்ந்து கொள்ளும்.)","arabic":"كَلَّآۖ إِنَّهَا لَظَىٰ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5390,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā innahā laẓā ","translations":["By no means","Indeed, it (is)","surely a Flame of Hell","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","innahā","laẓā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2550],[2,2550,4360],[3,4360,5575]]}},{"name":"70:16","price":"16. அது தோல்களை எரித்து (மூளையை உருக்கி) விடும்.","arabic":"نَزَّاعَةٗ لِّلشَّوَىٰ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5391,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"nazzāʿatan lilshawā ","translations":["A remover","of the skin of the head","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["nazzāʿatan","lilshawā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1410],[2,1410,2775]]}},{"name":"70:17","price":"17. புறம்காட்டிச் சென்று புறக்கணித்தவர்களை எல்லாம் அது அழைக்கும்.","arabic":"تَدۡعُواْ مَنۡ أَدۡبَرَ وَتَوَلَّىٰ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5392,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"tadʿū man adbara watawallā ","translations":["Inviting","(him) who","turned his back","and went away","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["tadʿū","man","adbara","watawallā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,850],[2,850,1240],[3,1240,2130],[4,2130,3475]]}},{"name":"70:18","price":"18. (பொருளைச்) சேகரித்து(ச் செலவு செய்யாது) பத்திரப்படுத்தி வைத்திருந்தவர்களையும் (தன்னிடம் அழைக்கும்).","arabic":"وَجَمَعَ فَأَوۡعَىٰٓ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5393,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wajamaʿa fa-awʿā ","translations":["And collected","and hoarded","(18)"],"transliterationArr":["wajamaʿa","fa-awʿā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,880],[2,880,2125]]}},{"name":"70:19","price":"19. மெய்யாகவே மனிதன் பதற்றக்காரனாகவே படைக்கப்பட்டுள்ளான்.","arabic":"۞ إِنَّ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنَ خُلِقَ هَلُوعًا","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5394,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"inna al-insāna khuliqa halūʿan ","translations":["Indeed","the man","was created","anxious ","(19)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","al-insāna","khuliqa","halūʿan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1300],[2,1300,3260],[3,3260,3960],[4,3960,5595]]}},{"name":"70:20","price":"20. ஏனென்றால், அவனை ஒரு தீங்கு அடைந்தால், (திடுக்கிட்டு) நடுங்குகிறான்.","arabic":"إِذَا مَسَّهُ ٱلشَّرُّ جَزُوعٗا","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5395,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"idhā massahu al-sharu jazūʿan ","translations":["When","touches him","the evil","distressed","(20)"],"transliterationArr":["idhā","massahu","al-sharu","jazūʿan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,590],[2,590,1350],[3,1350,2160],[4,2160,3755]]}},{"name":"70:21","price":"21. அவனை ஒரு நன்மை அடைந்தாலோ, அதை (தர்மம் செய்யாது) தடுத்துக் கொள்கிறான்.","arabic":"وَإِذَا مَسَّهُ ٱلۡخَيۡرُ مَنُوعًا","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5396,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā massahu al-khayru manūʿan ","translations":["And when","touches him","the good","withholding","(21)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","massahu","al-khayru","manūʿan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,850],[2,850,1610],[3,1610,2460],[4,2460,3925]]}},{"name":"70:22","price":"22. ஆயினும், தொழுகையாளிகளைத் தவிர.","arabic":"إِلَّا ٱلۡمُصَلِّينَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5397,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"illā al-muṣalīna ","translations":["Except","those who pray ","(22)"],"transliterationArr":["illā","al-muṣalīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,530],[2,530,3765]]}},{"name":"70:23","price":"23. அவர்கள் தங்கள் தொழுகையைத் தவறாது தொழுது வருவார்கள்.","arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ عَلَىٰ صَلَاتِهِمۡ دَآئِمُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5398,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhīna hum ʿalā ṣalātihim dāimūna ","translations":["Those who","[they]","at","their prayer","(are) constant","(23)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhīna","hum","ʿalā","ṣalātihim","dāimūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1220],[2,1220,1560],[3,1560,2050],[4,2050,3430],[5,3430,7895]]}},{"name":"70:24","price":"24. அவர்களுடைய பொருள்களில் (ஏழைகளுக்குக்) குறிப்பிட்ட பங்கு உண்டு.","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ فِيٓ أَمۡوَٰلِهِمۡ حَقّٞ مَّعۡلُومٞ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5399,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-alladhīna fī amwālihim ḥaqqun maʿlūmun ","translations":["And those who","in","their wealth","(is) a right","known","(24)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-alladhīna","fī","amwālihim","ḥaqqun","maʿlūmun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1170],[2,1170,2820],[3,2820,4090],[4,4090,4770],[5,4770,8485]]}},{"name":"70:25","price":"25. அதைக் கேட்பவர்களுக்கும் (வெட்கத்தால் கேட்காத) வரியவர்களுக்கும் (கொடுப்பார்கள்).","arabic":"لِّلسَّآئِلِ وَٱلۡمَحۡرُومِ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5400,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"lilssāili wal-maḥrūmi ","translations":["For the one who asks","and the deprived","(25)"],"transliterationArr":["lilssāili","wal-maḥrūmi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2780],[2,2780,6375]]}},{"name":"70:26","price":"26. கூலி கொடுக்கும் நாளையும் அவர்கள் உண்மை என்றே நம்புகின்றனர்.","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ يُصَدِّقُونَ بِيَوۡمِ ٱلدِّينِ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5401,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-alladhīna yuṣaddiqūna biyawmi al-dīni ","translations":["And those who","accept (the) truth","(of the) Day","(of) the Judgment","(26)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-alladhīna","yuṣaddiqūna","biyawmi","al-dīni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1200],[2,1200,2510],[3,2510,3360],[4,3360,5925]]}},{"name":"70:27","price":"27. (இவ்வாறிருந்தும்) அவர்கள் தங்கள் இறைவனின் வேதனைக்குப் பயந்து கொண்டே இருப்பார்கள்.","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ هُم مِّنۡ عَذَابِ رَبِّهِم مُّشۡفِقُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5402,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-alladhīna hum min ʿadhābi rabbihim mush'fiqūna ","translations":["And those who","[they]","of","(the) punishment","(of) their Lord","(are) fearful ","(27)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-alladhīna","hum","min","ʿadhābi","rabbihim","mush'fiqūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1200],[2,1200,1560],[3,1560,2630],[4,2630,3430],[5,3430,4850],[6,4850,8745]]}},{"name":"70:28","price":"28. (ஏனென்றால்,) நிச்சயமாகத் தங்கள் இறைவனின் வேதனை அச்சமற்றிருக்கக் கூடியதல்ல.","arabic":"إِنَّ عَذَابَ رَبِّهِمۡ غَيۡرُ مَأۡمُونٖ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5403,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"inna ʿadhāba rabbihim ghayru mamūnin ","translations":["Indeed","(the) punishment","(of) your Lord","(is) not","to be felt secure (of) ","(28)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","ʿadhāba","rabbihim","ghayru","mamūnin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1060],[2,1060,1890],[3,1890,2820],[4,2820,3470],[5,3470,6505]]}},{"name":"70:29","price":"29. அவர்கள், தங்கள் மர்மஸ்தானத்தையும் பாதுகாத்துக் கொள்வார்கள்.","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ لِفُرُوجِهِمۡ حَٰفِظُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5404,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-alladhīna hum lifurūjihim ḥāfiẓūna ","translations":["And those who","[they]","their modesty","(are) guardians","(29)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-alladhīna","hum","lifurūjihim","ḥāfiẓūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1100],[2,1100,1490],[3,1490,2880],[4,2880,5955]]}},{"name":"70:30","price":"30. ஆயினும், தங்கள் மனைவிகளிடத்திலும், தங்கள் அடிமைப் பெண்களிடத்திலும் தவிர. நிச்சயமாக அவர்கள் (இவர்களுடன் சம்பந்தப்படுவதைப் பற்றி) நிந்திக்கப்பட மாட்டார்கள்.","arabic":"إِلَّا عَلَىٰٓ أَزۡوَٰجِهِمۡ أَوۡ مَا مَلَكَتۡ أَيۡمَٰنُهُمۡ فَإِنَّهُمۡ غَيۡرُ مَلُومِينَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5405,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"illā ʿalā azwājihim aw mā malakat aymānuhum fa-innahum ghayru malūmīna ","translations":["Except","from","their spouses","or","what","they possess","rightfully","then indeed, they","(are) not","blameworthy","(30)"],"transliterationArr":["illā","ʿalā","azwājihim","aw","mā","malakat","aymānuhum","fa-innahum","ghayru","malūmīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,800],[2,800,2980],[3,2980,4420],[4,4420,4790],[5,4790,5170],[6,5170,5970],[7,5970,7340],[8,7340,9170],[9,9170,9750],[10,9750,12705]]}},{"name":"70:31","price":"31. இதைத்தவிர (மற்றெதையும்) எவரேனும் விரும்பினால், அத்தகையவர்கள் வரம்பு மீறியவர்களாவார்கள்.","arabic":"فَمَنِ ٱبۡتَغَىٰ وَرَآءَ ذَٰلِكَ فَأُوْلَٰٓئِكَ هُمُ ٱلۡعَادُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5406,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"famani ib'taghā warāa dhālika fa-ulāika humu al-ʿādūna ","translations":["But whoever","seeks","beyond","that","then those","[they]","(are) the transgressors ","(31)"],"transliterationArr":["famani","ib'taghā","warāa","dhālika","fa-ulāika","humu","al-ʿādūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,590],[2,590,1440],[3,1440,3500],[4,3500,4240],[5,4240,6759],[6,6759,7099],[7,7099,10094]]}},{"name":"70:32","price":"32. இன்னும், எவர்கள், தங்களிடம் (நம்பி) ஒப்படைக்கப்பட்ட அமானிதப் பொருள்களையும், (தாங்கள் செய்த) வாக்குறுதிகளையும் பேணி, (யோக்கியமாக நடந்து) கொள்கிறார்களோ அவர்களும்,","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ لِأَمَٰنَٰتِهِمۡ وَعَهۡدِهِمۡ رَٰعُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5407,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-alladhīna hum li-amānātihim waʿahdihim rāʿūna ","translations":["And those who","[they]","of their trusts","and their promise","(are) observers","(32)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-alladhīna","hum","li-amānātihim","waʿahdihim","rāʿūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1230],[2,1230,1540],[3,1540,3340],[4,3340,4420],[5,4420,7235]]}},{"name":"70:33","price":"33. இன்னும், எவர்கள், தங்கள் சாட்சியத்தில் (தவறிழைக்காது) உறுதியாக இருக்கிறார்களோ அவர்களும்,","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ هُم بِشَهَٰدَٰتِهِمۡ قَآئِمُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5408,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-alladhīna hum bishahādātihim qāimūna ","translations":["And those who","[they]","in their testimonies","stand firm","(33)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-alladhīna","hum","bishahādātihim","qāimūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1160],[2,1160,2060],[3,2060,3940],[4,3940,8905]]}},{"name":"70:34","price":"34. இன்னும், எவர்கள் தொழுகையையும் கவனித்து(த் தவறாது) ஒழுங்காகத் தொழுது வருகிறார்களோ அவர்களும்,","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ عَلَىٰ صَلَاتِهِمۡ يُحَافِظُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5409,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-alladhīna hum ʿalā ṣalātihim yuḥāfiẓūna ","translations":["And those who","[they]","on","their prayer","keep a guard ","(34)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-alladhīna","hum","ʿalā","ṣalātihim","yuḥāfiẓūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1230],[2,1230,1600],[3,1600,2180],[4,2180,3350],[5,3350,7065]]}},{"name":"70:35","price":"35. ஆகிய இவர்கள்தான் சொர்க்கத்தில் கண்ணியப்படுத்தப்படுவார்கள்.","arabic":"أُوْلَٰٓئِكَ فِي جَنَّٰتٖ مُّكۡرَمُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5410,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"ulāika fī jannātin muk'ramūna ","translations":["Those","(will be) in","Gardens","honored","(35)"],"transliterationArr":["ulāika","fī","jannātin","muk'ramūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2530],[2,2530,2900],[3,2900,4920],[4,4920,8705]]}},{"name":"70:36","price":"36. (நபியே!) இந்நிராகரிப்பவர்களுக்கு என்ன சுதந்திரம்? (அவர்கள்) உமக்கு முன் ஓடி வருகின்றனர்!","arabic":"فَمَالِ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُواْ قِبَلَكَ مُهۡطِعِينَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5411,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"famāli alladhīna kafarū qibalaka muh'ṭiʿīna ","translations":["So what is with","those who","disbelieve","before you","(they) hasten","(36)"],"transliterationArr":["famāli","alladhīna","kafarū","qibalaka","muh'ṭiʿīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,790],[2,790,1700],[3,1700,2520],[4,2520,3390],[5,3390,6335]]}},{"name":"70:37","price":"37. வலது புறமிருந்தும், இடது புறமிருந்தும் கூட்டம் கூட்டமாக (ஓடி வருகின்றனர்).","arabic":"عَنِ ٱلۡيَمِينِ وَعَنِ ٱلشِّمَالِ عِزِينَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5412,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿani al-yamīni waʿani al-shimāli ʿizīna ","translations":["On","the right","and on","the left","(in) separate groups","(37)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿani","al-yamīni","waʿani","al-shimāli","ʿizīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,450],[2,450,1420],[3,1420,1990],[4,1990,2950],[5,2950,5635]]}},{"name":"70:38","price":"38. அவர்களில் ஒவ்வொருவரும் இன்பம் தரும் சொர்க்கத்தில் நுழைந்து விடலாமென்று ஆசைப்படுகின்றனரா?","arabic":"أَيَطۡمَعُ كُلُّ ٱمۡرِيٕٖ مِّنۡهُمۡ أَن يُدۡخَلَ جَنَّةَ نَعِيمٖ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5413,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"ayaṭmaʿu kullu im'ri-in min'hum an yud'khala jannata naʿīmin ","translations":["Does long","every","person","among them","that","he enters","a Garden","(of) Delight","(38)"],"transliterationArr":["ayaṭmaʿu","kullu","im'ri-in","min'hum","an","yud'khala","jannata","naʿīmin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1040],[2,1040,1600],[3,1600,2250],[4,2250,3800],[5,3800,5730],[6,5730,7380],[7,7380,10085]]}},{"name":"70:39","price":"39. அது ஆகப்போவதில்லை. அவர்கள் அறிந்த ஓர் (அற்ப) வஸ்துவிலிருந்தே நாம் அவர்களைப் படைத்திருக்கிறோம்.","arabic":"كَلَّآۖ إِنَّا خَلَقۡنَٰهُم مِّمَّا يَعۡلَمُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5414,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā innā khalaqnāhum mimmā yaʿlamūna ","translations":["By no means","Indeed, We","[We] have created them","from what","they know","(39)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","innā","khalaqnāhum","mimmā","yaʿlamūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,970],[2,970,3170],[3,3170,4490],[4,4490,6550],[5,6550,9785]]}},{"name":"70:40","price":"40. கிழக்கு மற்றும் மேற்குத் திசையின் இறைவன்மீது சத்தியமாக! நிச்சயமாக நாம் (நம் விருப்பப்படி செய்ய) ஆற்றலுடையோம்!","arabic":"فَلَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِرَبِّ ٱلۡمَشَٰرِقِ وَٱلۡمَغَٰرِبِ إِنَّا لَقَٰدِرُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5415,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"falā uq'simu birabbi al-mashāriqi wal-maghāribi innā laqādirūna ","translations":["But nay","I swear","by (the) Lord","(of) the risings","and the settings","that We","(are) surely Able","(40)"],"transliterationArr":["falā","uq'simu","birabbi","al-mashāriqi","wal-maghāribi","innā","laqādirūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1860],[2,1860,2690],[3,2690,3440],[4,3440,4650],[5,4650,5970],[6,5970,7440],[7,7440,10645]]}},{"name":"70:41","price":"41. (இவர்களை நீக்கி) இவர்களைவிட மேலானவர்களை மாற்றிவிடவும் (ஆற்றலுடையோம்!) இதில் நாம் இயலாதவர்களல்ல.","arabic":"عَلَىٰٓ أَن نُّبَدِّلَ خَيۡرٗا مِّنۡهُمۡ وَمَا نَحۡنُ بِمَسۡبُوقِينَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5416,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿalā an nubaddila khayran min'hum wamā naḥnu bimasbūqīna ","translations":["[On]","to","[We] replace","(with) better","than them","and not","We","(are) to be outrun","(41)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿalā","an","nubaddila","khayran","min'hum","wamā","naḥnu","bimasbūqīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1960],[2,1960,2310],[3,2310,3890],[4,3890,4530],[5,4530,6210],[6,6210,6760],[7,6760,7370],[8,7370,10855]]}},{"name":"70:42","price":"42. ஆகவே, (நபியே!) அவர்களுக்கு வாக்களிக்கப்பட்ட நாளை அவர்கள் சந்திக்கும் வரை, அவர்கள் விளையாடிக்கொண்டும், (வீண் காரியங்களில்) ஆழ்ந்து கிடக்குமாறும் அவர்களை நீர் விட்டுவிடுவீராக.","arabic":"فَذَرۡهُمۡ يَخُوضُواْ وَيَلۡعَبُواْ حَتَّىٰ يُلَٰقُواْ يَوۡمَهُمُ ٱلَّذِي يُوعَدُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5417,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"fadharhum yakhūḍū wayalʿabū ḥattā yulāqū yawmahumu alladhī yūʿadūna ","translations":["So leave them","(to) converse vainly","and amuse themselves","until","they meet","their Day","which","they are promised","(42)"],"transliterationArr":["fadharhum","yakhūḍū","wayalʿabū","ḥattā","yulāqū","yawmahumu","alladhī","yūʿadūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1000],[2,1000,2130],[3,2130,3210],[4,3210,4030],[5,4030,5020],[6,5020,6070],[7,6070,6950],[8,6950,10115]]}},{"name":"70:43","price":"43. (நபியே!) அவர்களுக்கு ஒரு நாளை நீர் ஞாபகமூட்டுவீராக. (சிலை வணங்குபவர்கள் தங்கள் திருநாள்களில் பூஜைக்காக நட்டுவைக்கப்பட்ட) கொடிகளின் பக்கம் விரைந்தோடுவதைப் போலவே, சமாதிகளிலிருந்து வெளிப்பட்டு (ஹஷ்ருடைய மைதானத்திற்கு) வெகு தீவிரமாகச் செல்வார்கள்.","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يَخۡرُجُونَ مِنَ ٱلۡأَجۡدَاثِ سِرَاعٗا كَأَنَّهُمۡ إِلَىٰ نُصُبٖ يُوفِضُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5418,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"yawma yakhrujūna mina al-ajdāthi sirāʿan ka-annahum ilā nuṣubin yūfiḍūna ","translations":["(The) Day","they will come out","from","the graves","rapidly","as if they (were)","to","a goal","hastening","(43)"],"transliterationArr":["yawma","yakhrujūna","mina","al-ajdāthi","sirāʿan","ka-annahum","ilā","nuṣubin","yūfiḍūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,690],[2,690,1770],[3,1770,2140],[4,2140,3350],[5,3350,4950],[6,4950,6910],[7,6910,7510],[8,7510,8950],[9,8950,12385]]}},{"name":"70:44","price":"44. (அந்நாளில்) பயந்த பார்வையுடன் ஓடுவார்கள். இழிவும் அவர்களைச் சூழ்ந்து கொள்ளும். (நபியே!) இந்நாள்தான் அவர்களுக்கு வாக்களிக்கப்பட்ட நாளாகும்.","arabic":"خَٰشِعَةً أَبۡصَٰرُهُمۡ تَرۡهَقُهُمۡ ذِلَّةٞۚ ذَٰلِكَ ٱلۡيَوۡمُ ٱلَّذِي كَانُواْ يُوعَدُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5419,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"khāshiʿatan abṣāruhum tarhaquhum dhillatun dhālika al-yawmu alladhī kānū yūʿadūna ","translations":["Humbled","their eyesights","will cover them","humiliation","That","(is) the Day","which","they were","promised","(44)"],"transliterationArr":["khāshiʿatan","abṣāruhum","tarhaquhum","dhillatun","dhālika","al-yawmu","alladhī","kānū","yūʿadūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1000],[2,1000,2620],[3,2620,3740],[4,3740,5200],[5,5200,6050],[6,6050,6780],[7,6780,7800],[8,7800,8750],[9,8750,14165]]}}],"chapter":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij","Chapter Al-Ma'arij","Ma'arij","Surah Ma'arij","Chapter Ma'arij","Al Ma'arij","Surah Al Ma'arij","Chapter Al Ma'arij","Surah 70","Chapter 70","The Ascending Stairways","المعارج"],"version":{"key":"tamil_baqavi","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"ta","version":"1.0.1","last_update":1609966800,"title":"Tamil Translation - Abdulhamid Albaqoi","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Tamil by Sh. Abdulhamid Albaqoi"}}